column1:
This file contains spreadsheets showing the structure of tables (.csv files) from the Google Cluster Data.
Each sheet is just a sample from the first file inside the subdirectory with the same name of the sheet itself.

For additional information and to download the original trace files, 
check out https://github.com/google/cluster-data/blob/master/ClusterData2011_2.md

These trace files can be read by CloudSim Plus using classes available at the org.cloudsimplus.traces.google package.
Also check out the org.cloudsimplus.examples.googletraces package inside the examples module.
